item.title: Community
item.description: Are you working on a healthcare project that could benefit from advanced data management and analytics? JupyterHealth invites innovators, developers, researchers, clinicians, and technologists to engage with our platform.

item.title: JupyterHealth Core Capabilities
item.description: JupyterHealth leverages its expertise across four pivotal domains, ensuring a comprehensive and integrated approach to healthcare data management and analysis. Each domain is designed to empower researchers, clinicians, and data scientists with the tools they need to excel in their fields.
